  "subject": "0.3.1 release",
  "commit_message": "0.3.1 release\n\n- fix pipeline\n- cache rbac mappings from keycloak\n- fix new cached rbac implementation\n- fix new cached rbac implementation V2\n- fix new cached rbac implementation V3\n- fix release metadata\n- update spring-boot 3.3 patch version\n- publish snapshots on merge (instead of releases)\n- add unique snapshot Docker image tags to portal-ng repos\n- fix jar publishing\n\nIssue-ID: PORTALNG-182\nChange-Id: I712dcd31497f4e5354103200f7e49888f36946eb\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
